 Instructions

1- Create a MEAN version of the Games application to display all the games and a single game.

2- Create a MEAN version of the SchoolDB application to display all the students and a single student.

3- Create a MEAN version of your weekend application. The application should have the ability to display all your documents and a single document.

4- Use at least one angular pipe in each of the above projects.

Make sure all your applications follow the proper SoC covered in class. 